text: Watchhouse in the Carpathians (Hungarian: Őrház a Kárpátokban) is a 1914 Hungarian drama movie directed by first time director Alexander Korda and Gyula Zilahy. It stars Anna Hadrik and Gusztáv Vándory. ==Other websites== * Category:1914 drama movies Category:Hungarian silent movies Category:Movies directed by Alexander Korda
title: Watchhouse in the Carpathians
